      <title>特朗普幽灵引发最后一轮利率调整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/specter-of-trump-spurs-a-final-round-of-interest-rate-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫引发全球贸易动荡的可能性上升之前，四大洲的央行将在未来一周对借贷成本做出最后一系列调整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/specter-of-trump-spurs-a-final-round-of-interest-rate-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
